modShortDescription: Adds a lively and fully functional parking barrier, craftable in the workbench for construction and decoration enthusiasts.
modDescription:
Adds a lively and fully functional parking barrier, craftable in the workbench for construction and decoration enthusiasts.

To install this mod unzip the folder and copy / paste it in your mod folder of the games. To find your mod folder ->: C: \\ Program Files (x86) \\ Steam \\ steamapps \\ common \\ 7daystodie or if you install it on another disk ->: D: \\ SteamLibrary \\ steamapps \\ common \\ 7 Days To Die

Do not hesitate to contact me in case of problem. Leave a little comment to give me your opinion.
